## API Surface

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|--------|----------|---------|
| GET | `/api/stream` | SSE event stream |
| GET | `/api/status` | Current pipeline state |
| POST | `/api/run` | Start pipeline (stepStart, stepEnd, ticketKey, filter) |
| POST | `/api/run/step/:num` | Run single step |
| GET | `/api/runs` | Recent run history |
| GET | `/api/runs/:id` | Single run detail |
| GET | `/api/runs/:id/steps/:num` | Step result with logs + artifacts |
| GET | `/api/schedules` | List schedules |
| POST | `/api/schedules` | Create schedule |
| PUT | `/api/schedules/:id` | Update schedule |
| DELETE | `/api/schedules/:id` | Delete schedule |
| POST | `/api/schedules/:id/toggle` | Toggle schedule on/off |
